-- Cordoba Cites Panama, Costa Rica Mila Interest, Portafolio Says
-- B y   C h r i s t i n e   J e n k i n s
-- 2012-06-01T13:42:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-01/cordoba-cites-panama-costa-rica-mila-interest-portafolio-says.html
Panama’s and  Costa Rica ’s bourses are
interested in joining Mila, as the Andean integrated market is
known, according to Juan Pablo Cordoba, president of  Bolsa de
Valores de Colombia , which operates the country’s main stock
exchange. Portafolio  reported  his comments at an event he
attended.  To contact the reporter on this story:
